WASD / Arrow Keys for movement.

Left click to light attack.

Space to heavy attack.

T in traits menu to see active traits, or T in game to see data.

E to pick up items.

R to parry/reload.

V to switch between weapon properties. (Unused currently)

C to use aux

Q to shove.

X to drop/cancel scrapping/cancel crafting

0 to prepare thyself.



Sandbox Only:

9 - Open command terminal.
